shape: sequence_diagram

Radar as RadarController
Thread as ProcessorThread
Act as ActivityPipeline
Gate as MonitorGate
Resp as RespiratoryPipelineV2
GUI as MainWindow

Radar -> Thread: enqueue fft_frame
Thread -> Act: process_frame(frame)
Act -> Thread: occ_dict
Thread -> Gate: evaluate zone/status

Gate -> Resp: eligible => process(occ_dict, frames)
Resp -> Thread: resp_dict
Gate -> Thread: not eligible => _reset_state()

Thread -> GUI: data_ready(occ_dict, resp_dict)
GUI -> GUI: update cards/plots/layout
